Package services.patient

Class AppointmentManagementServicePatient

java.lang.Object
services.AppointmentManagementService
services.patient.AppointmentManagementServicePatient
public class AppointmentManagementServicePatient extends AppointmentManagementService
This Service AppointmentManagementServicePatient class handles the business logic of the app for Patient Menu and inherits all behaviours and properties from AppointmentManagementService It allows current patient to schedule, reschedule, cancel schedule currentUser to be initialized with the Patient logged in with type Patient and will be used throughout this service doctorList type HashMap to map each choice as key to the value of doctor with type Doctor
